{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/runmanager/issues/21/comments/12743212.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/runmanager/issues/21#comment-12743212"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/runmanager/issues/21.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 21, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/runmanager.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/runmanager"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{9b4f21e6-54b0-41ea-8f01-db1919f2f790}ts=249918"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "runmanager", "full_name": "labscript_suite/runmanager", "uuid": "{9b4f21e6-54b0-41ea-8f01-db1919f2f790}"}, "title": "Globals are sorted by \"Delete\" rather than \"Name\""}, "content": {"raw": "Actually the reason they are sorted by name is because I had them inserted in that order:\n\n\n```\n#!python\n\n        globals = runmanager.get_globals({self.group_name: self.globals_file})[self.group_name]\n        globals_items = list(globals.items())\n        globals_items.sort()  # Ensure globals ordered alphabetically at load time\n```\n\nBut now I've changed it so that the sorting is done after insertion, with:\n\n\n```\n#!python\n\n        # Sort by name:\n        self.ui.treeView_globals.sortByColumn(self.GLOBALS_COL_NAME, QtCore.Qt.AscendingOrder)\n```", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Actually the reason they are sorted by name is because I had them inserted in that order:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-python\"><pre><span></span>        <span class=\"nb\">globals</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">runmanager</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">get_globals</span><span class=\"p\">({</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">group_name</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">globals_file</span><span class=\"p\">})[</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">group_name</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">globals_items</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">list</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">globals</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">items</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">globals_items</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sort</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>  <span class=\"c1\"># Ensure globals ordered alphabetically at load time</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>But now I've changed it so that the sorting is done after insertion, with:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-python\"><pre><span></span>        <span class=\"c1\"># Sort by name:</span>\n        <span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ui</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">treeView_globals</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sortByColumn</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">GLOBALS_COL_NAME</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">QtCore</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Qt</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">AscendingOrder</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-10-02T23:57:28.805356+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Chris Billington", "uuid": "{e363c5a9-5075-4656-afb5-88bd6a6dceeb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Be363c5a9-5075-4656-afb5-88bd6a6dceeb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Be363c5a9-5075-4656-afb5-88bd6a6dceeb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9238baf7300c41c0e7294db922899e6ad=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsCB-1.png"}}, "nickname": "cbillington", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:cbf1bc43-1dc2-477b-9e25-1a8f40fd7ee3"}, "updated_on": null, "typ